    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.85a"/>
                
                <note type="curatorial">13  Neihardt Collection</note>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">ADELE MEHL BURNETT
                        <lb/>
                    115 WEST HUDSON
                        <lb/>
                    PITTSBURG, KANSAS</hi>
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>May 26, 1958</dateline>
                
                    <salute>Dear Dr. Neihardt</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I was shocked to learn of the death of Mrs. Neihardt. She was wonderful woman, a gifted woman, a rarely charming woman. I'm sorry I wasn't close enough to talk with her often. Something within her reached out to me and comforted and inspired me.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Very Sincerely</salute>
                
                    <signed>Adele Mehl Burnett</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
            
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.85b"/>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    PITTSBURG, KANSAS
                    MAY 26
                    4 - PM
                    1958
                </ab>
                <figure>
                    <figDesc>3 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                    <p>U.S. POSTAGE 3Â¢
                    IN GOD WE TRUST
                    LIBERTY</p>
                </figure>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Route 6</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Columbia, Missouri</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </ab>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">8<del>6</del><add>5</add></fw>
                
